<p>I would like to initialize an element whenever it is rendered using iron pages.</p>  <p>In the jsbin do the below operation</p>  <ol> <li>Click 'Toggle'</li> <li>Click 'Toggle step'</li> <li>Click 'Toggle'</li> <li>Click 'Toggle' again</li> </ol>  <p>I expect to see 'step a'. As the x-example assigns 'step="a"'. However I see 'step b'. Is there any way to show 'step a' whenever y-example is shown?</p>  <p>jsbin: <a href="http://jsbin.com/regapemoqe/1/edit?html,output" rel="nofollow">http://jsbin.com/regapemoqe/1/edit?html,output</a></p>  <p>Code:          </p>  <pre><code>  &lt;meta charset="utf-8"&gt;    &lt;base href="http://polymer-magic-server.appspot.com/components/"&gt;    &lt;script src="webcomponentsjs/webcomponents-lite.min.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;    &lt;link href="polymer/polymer.html" rel="import"&gt;   &lt;link href="iron-pages/iron-pages.html" rel="import"&gt;     &lt;style&gt;     body {       font-family: sans-serif;     }   &lt;/style&gt;  &lt;/head&gt; &lt;body&gt;  &lt;x-example&gt;&lt;/x-example&gt;  &lt;dom-module id="x-example"&gt;   &lt;style&gt;     :host {       display: block;     }     &lt;/style&gt;   &lt;template&gt;      &lt;button on-click="toggleSelection"&gt;Toggle&lt;/button&gt;     &lt;iron-pages          attr-for-selected="data-route"          selected=[[selected]]&gt;       &lt;section data-route="one"&gt;         &lt;p&gt;This is the one&lt;/p&gt;       &lt;/section&gt;       &lt;section data-route="two"&gt;         &lt;p&gt;This is the other one&lt;/p&gt;         &lt;y-example             step="a"&gt;&lt;/y-example&gt;       &lt;/section&gt;       &lt;/iron-pages&gt;    &lt;/template&gt;   &lt;script&gt;      // only need this when both (1) in the main document and (2) on non-Chrome browsers     addEventListener('WebComponentsReady', function() {        Polymer({         is: "x-example",         properties: {           selected: {             type: String,             value: 'one'           }         },         toggleSelection: function() {           this.selected = (this.selected == 'one')?'two':'one';         }       });     });    &lt;/script&gt; &lt;/dom-module&gt;  &lt;dom-module id="y-example"&gt;   &lt;style&gt;     :host {       display: block;     }   &lt;/style&gt;    &lt;template&gt;      &lt;iron-pages           attr-for-selected="data-step"           selected="[[step]]"&gt;       &lt;section data-step="a"&gt;&lt;p&gt;This is step a&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/section&gt;       &lt;section data-step="b"&gt;&lt;p&gt;This is step b&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/section&gt;           &lt;/iron-pages&gt;     &lt;button on-click="toggleStep"&gt;Toggle step&lt;/button&gt;   &lt;/template&gt;   &lt;script&gt;     addEventListener('WebComponentsReady', function() {       Polymer({         is: "y-example",         properties: {           step: {             type: String,             value: 'a'           }         },         toggleStep: function() {           this.step = (this.step == 'a')?'b':'a'         }       });     });   &lt;/script&gt; &lt;/dom-module&gt;  &lt;/body&gt; </code></pre>